text: Alex Moore (21 December 1918 – 28 August 1989) was an Australian rules footballer who played for the Collingwood Football Club in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * *Profile at CollingwoodFC.com.au Category:1918 births Category:1989 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Collingwood Football Club players
